{"id":26379,"date":"2020-12-21T18:07:52","date_gmt":"2020-12-21T18:07:52","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/?page_id=26379"},"modified":"2021-07-05T18:31:44","modified_gmt":"2021-07-05T18:31:44","slug":"create-your-own-scholarship","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/create-your-own-scholarship\/","title":{"rendered":"Create Your Own Scholarship"},"content":{"rendered":"\n\n\t<h1><strong>Create Your Own Scholarship<\/strong><\/h1>\n\t<h4>Pay it forward. Sponsor an American Muslim student pursuing a degree in media, film, law, or policy.<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/Salina-Nasir.jpg\" alt=\"Salina Nasir\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"850\" width=\"1280\" title=\"Salina Nasir\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"  \/>\n\t<p>With ISF&#8217;s Create Your Own Scholarship program, you can establish a scholarship in honor of your family, company, university, or organization, without any of the heavy legal and administrative paperwork.<\/p>\n\n<p>Was the key to your success your education and\/or the support of a mentor or friend? Create a scholarship in your name and provide the same opportunity for an accomplished scholar improving the world for American Muslims and marginalized populations.<\/p>\n\t<h4><b>WHY WOULD I ESTABLISH A SCHOLARSHIP?<\/b><\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-grad-hat.png\" alt=\"ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-grad-hat\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"357\" width=\"357\" title=\"ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-grad-hat\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"  \/>\n\t\n<p>Directly support young American Muslims who are changing the narrative about Islam.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-heart.png\" alt=\"ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-heart\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"357\" width=\"357\" title=\"ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-heart\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"  \/>\n\t\n<p>Gift a family member or loved one who impacted your education and career with a scholarship established in their name.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-masjid.png\" alt=\"ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-masjid\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"357\" width=\"357\" title=\"ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-masjid\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"  \/>\n\t\n<p>Honor a parent, child, or loved one who was passionate about social justice, education, and paying it forward.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-bullhorn.png\" alt=\"ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-bullhorn\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"357\" width=\"357\" title=\"ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-bullhorn\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"  \/>\n\t\n<p>Show the community that your company cares. Establish a scholarship in honor of your business or organization.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-trophy.png\" alt=\"ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-trophy\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"357\" width=\"357\" title=\"ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-trophy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"  \/>\n\t\n<p>Demonstrate your gratitude to an individual (imam, teacher, volunteer leader, etc.) who made a big impact in your life.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-give.png\" alt=\"ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-give\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"357\" width=\"357\" title=\"ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-give\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"  \/>\n\t\n<p>Establish an ongoing charity for yourself or a loved one to make a lasting and significant impact in this lifetime and the next.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-kids.png\" alt=\"ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-kids\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"357\" width=\"357\" title=\"ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-kids\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"  \/>\n\t\n<p>Do your part to ensure your children and the next generation live in a more equitable and just world.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-gavel.png\" alt=\"ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-gavel\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"357\" width=\"357\" title=\"ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-gavel\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"  \/>\n\t\n<p>Fund policy students pursuing their education and career in government, law, or policy to increase American Muslim representation where it matters most.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-film.png\" alt=\"ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-film\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"357\" width=\"357\" title=\"ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-film\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"  \/>\n\t\n<p>Increase representation of American Muslims in film and television to create more accurate and less damaging portrayals of our community.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-news.png\" alt=\"ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-news\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"357\" width=\"357\" title=\"ISF-Create-Your-Own-Scholarship-Landing-Page-icon-news\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"  \/>\n\t\n<p>Decrease the harm created by inaccurate reporting by supporting scholars who are changing the narrative.<\/p>\n\t<h4><b>HOW DOES THE PROCESS WORK?<\/b><b><\/b><\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/steps_img_steps.png\" alt=\"steps_img_steps\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"228\" width=\"1011\" title=\"steps_img_steps\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"  \/>\n\t<h4><b>STEP ONE: SELECT AN ISF PROGRAM<\/b><\/h4>\n\t\n\n<ul>\n<li>Sponsor an annual scholarship<\/li>\n<li>Minimum amount for scholarship sponsorship is $3,000<\/li>\n<li>Law scholarships start at $5,000<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n<p>During the first year, sponsor a scholarship in an amount greater than or equal to $3,000. In the second year and years following, your financial contribution will be split: 50% of the annual funds will be awarded to scholars and 50% will be invested in ISF&#8217;s Endowment Fund.<\/p>\n\n<p>Create your own legacy through ISF&#8217;s Endowment Fund. The minimum contribution to initiate an endowment is $50,000. Your scholarship(s) will be awarded after the first year upon accumulation of investment funds.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/Lila-Hassan.-Journalism.jpg\" alt=\"Lila Hassan. Journalism\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"1600\" width=\"1200\" title=\"Lila Hassan. Journalism\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"  \/>\n\t<h4><b>STEP TWO: CUSTOMIZE AMOUNT<\/b><\/h4>\n\t\n\n<p>Scholarships range from $3,000-$10,000<br \/>Law scholarships begin at $5,000<br \/>Minimum endowment funds are $50,000<\/p>\n\t<h4><b>STEP THREE: NAME SCHOLARSHIP<\/b><\/h4>\n\t<p>What will you name your scholarship? Choose to name it after yourself or in honor of another person, family member, loved one, or organization. Examples include: The ISF Khan Scholarship or The ISF Masjid al-Haram Scholarship.<\/p>\n\t<h4><b>STEP FOUR: DEFINE CRITERIA<\/b><\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/Rami-Koujah.-Law-scaled-1.jpg\" alt=\"Rami Koujah. Law\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"2557\" width=\"2560\" title=\"Rami Koujah. Law\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"  \/>\n\t\n\n<p><b>Scholarship Field:<\/b> Donors can select a specific ISF-supported major for your sponsored scholarship (e.g. The ISF Khan Journalism Scholarship).<\/p>\n\n<p><b>Scholarship Region:\u00a0<\/b>Donors can choose a region where you&#8217;d like to award your scholarship (e.g. The ISF-Khan Greater Boston Region Scholarship).<\/p>\n\t<h4><b>STEP FIVE: SELECT PAYMENT PLAN<\/b><\/h4>\n\t\n\n<ul>\n<li>Scholarships: Pay in full with one installment on May 1st of each year.<\/li>\n<li>Endowment: Pay as soon as you can to increase the investment funds. Please contact us for more information to set up your fund.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<p>We offer various payment options to make scholarship sponsorship convenient and affordable. Please contact us for more information about how to schedule your installment payments.<\/p>\n\n<p>ISF will collect funds from donors and provide tax deductible receipts. We can discuss this on our introductory call.<\/p>\n\t<h5>Schedule Call<\/h5>\n<p>I would like to schedule a meeting with ISF&#8217;s Director to discuss how to create my scholarship.<\/p>\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/calendly.com\/meet-with-isf\" target=\"_blank\" role=\"button\" rel=\"noopener\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tSCHEDULE\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t<h5>Get Started<\/h5>\n<p>I&#8217;m ready to go! Please take me to the donation form to establish my scholarship.<\/p>\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.z2systems.com\/np\/clients\/islamicscholarshipfund\/donation.jsp?campaign=16&#038;&#038;test=true\" target=\"_blank\" role=\"button\" rel=\"noopener\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tGET STARTED\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t<h5>Other Ways to Give<\/h5>\n<p>I&#8217;m not ready to create a scholarship, but would like to give to ISF.<\/p>\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/donate\/\" target=\"_blank\" role=\"button\" rel=\"noopener\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tLEARN MORE\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Create Your Own Scholarship Pay it forward. Sponsor an American Muslim student pursuing a degree in media, film, law, or policy. With ISF&#8217;s Create Your Own Scholarship program, you can establish a scholarship in honor of your family, company, university, or organization, without any of the heavy legal and administrative paperwork. Was the key to&hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v21.7 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Create Your Own Scholarship - Islamic Scholarship Fund<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/create-your-own-scholarship\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Create Your Own Scholarship - Islamic Scholarship Fund\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Create Your Own Scholarship Pay it forwa